{"tid":705000,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"好自卑","createTime":"2018-06-16T18:02:37.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-17T01:48:05.000Z","uid":8638,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"c976880b76847fc770302ff3d5c4e85f9b3f121f","tid":705000,"uid":8638,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T18:02:37.000Z","msg":"份人內向 淨係對住好熟既人先會多野講啲 9up下 但一對住唔熟既人個腦就會一片空白 一大堆人既時候就會好不安 比人話好小野講好靜 加上天生西西地面 所以覺得自己好唔討喜 人地會覺得我好悶<br />\n自己本身個樣普通 但身邊全部都係靚女 開朗又識交際 好多時候外人對我同佢既對待有對比 我就會暗底覺得唔開心 但從來都唔會同fd講原來我會因為咁唔開心 佢仲會同我講有太多人追真係好煩 仲數比我聽 我心諗我一個都無<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算係性格外向既肥婆都好 我都覺得羡慕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我有試過扮social啲笑多啲 但我返到屋企覺得好攰好辛苦.. 從來都無都其他人講過有幾憎自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e74c02c3b8de7ff547dde9f7a93e0bc7a76e0db9","tid":705000,"uid":148185,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T18:04:05.000Z","msg":"做番自己最吸引<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90ac20cff06977895dde05262f7ed318da7a384f","tid":705000,"uid":156592,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T18:04:48.000Z","msg":"同你一樣，不過我係男仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9e510ef11774ed140ab12091c1cccc5b0b935c6b","tid":705000,"uid":110112,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T18:07:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77034d817524b54464d90ebae3cd8bdea7132f69","tid":705000,"uid":10277,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-16T18:08:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/06/17/020758_c91704312f5ce3ab61b62b564e1bff7b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F06%2F17%2F020758_c91704312